metadata.name: A.I. Grace
metadata.description:
Inorganic world will become LIFE. 
Imagine Artificial Intelligence and Nature in one place, in complete symbiosis.
Nature is planted deeper in their system.

In this tropical paradise A.I. evolves dynamically as it learns and grows each time it interacts with organic life, by constructing this universe by itself. 
The same as symbolic flamingos, A.I. is experiencing GRACE and BALANCE.

Collector will receive 1920x1080 MP4 file and 4 high quality rendered scenes from the animation.
